Package plang.parser

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Parser  
    ParserFactory
    Supplied to a AbstractParser to allow for the use of different implementation of parser without altering the other parsers.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractParser<T extends Node>
    Abstract helper for implementing Parsers
    AssignmentParser
    Parses an assignment
    CallParser
    Parsing call expressions (or statements..)
    CompareParser
    Parse a comparsion
    DefaultParserFactory
    Default implementation of ParserFactory.
    ExpressionParser
    Parses an expression
    ExpressionsParser
    Parse a list of expressions
    FactorParser
    Parses a Factor (the leaf of a expression)
    IfParser
    Parse an if-statement
    StatementParser
    Parses a statement
    StatementsParser
    Parse a list of statements
    TermParser
    Parses a term and returns an ExpressionNode (if not optimized) but allow for precedence rules to apply.
